- The destroy handler is implemented in app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/MediaController.php as:

- This controller is the one referenced by routes/api.php for the /v1/media/{medium} endpoint (Route::apiResource('media', MediaController::class)->only(['store', 'destroy']);).
